        <div class="content-body">
          <p>Understanding where you stand relative to your competitors is the first step toward gaining a real advantage. We map your competitive landscape — products, pricing, positioning, market share, and customer sentiment — so your leadership team can make strategic decisions grounded in evidence rather than assumptions.</p>
          <p>Our analysis goes beyond surface-level comparisons. We dig into competitor strengths, weaknesses, go-to-market strategies, and customer reviews to identify the gaps and opportunities that matter most. The result is a clear picture of where you can differentiate and where you need to close the distance.</p>
          <p>Every engagement ends with a prioritized set of recommendations your team can act on immediately. We highlight the highest-impact moves — whether that means adjusting your pricing model, repositioning a product line, or doubling down on an underserved segment — and provide the supporting data to build internal alignment.</p>
        </div>

